quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  59,10,"(And it also belongs to) those who came after them, and who pray: “Lord, forgive us and our brethren who have preceded us in faith, and do not put in our hearts any rancour towards those who believe. Lord, You are the Most Tender, the Most Compassionate.”",footnotes:181986:1,footnotes:181987:2